			<li>FreeBSD PCBSD</li>
			<li>Mac OS X El Capitan, Yosemite, Maverick, Mountain Lion</li>
		</ul>

		<p>Snowmix has been tested to run on the following <a href="[HOME]Intro/requirements.html#hardware">architectures</a>:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>i386, i586, i686</li>
			<li>amd64/x86_64</li>
